<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٣٥٧٦]</span> خُزَيْمةُ بنُ شجرةَ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عن عَطاءٍ، قولَه.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَوى عَنه الثَّوريُّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٣٥٧٧]</span> خُزَيْمةُ بنُ مُحمدِ بنِ عُمارةَ بنِ خُزَيمةَ بنِ ثابتٍ الأنْصاريُّ، الخَطْميُّ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>عن أبيهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>رَوى عنه عبدُ اللَّه بنُ محمدِ بنِ عِمرانَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٣٥٧٨]</span> خُزَيْمةُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>عن عائشةَ بنتِ سَعدٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>رَوى عنه سعيدُ بنُ أبي هِلالٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
